title: Senate approves temporary spending bill; House to follow
text:
> Top News Senate approves temporary spending bill; House to follow Democratic presidential candidate Sen. Bernie Sanders, I-Vt., left, is interviewed as he leaves after a Senate vote on Capitol Hill in Washington, Wednesday, Sept. 30, 2015. to approved a stopgap spending bill to avert a government shutdown.
